You can simply ask Alexa to control your “Ceiling Fan”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “ART OF LIVING DESIGNS” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “ART OF LIVING DESIGNS” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “Ceiling Fan” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “Ceiling Fan” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Ceiling Fan” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on Ceiling Fan”
“Alexa, turn off Ceiling Fan”
“Alexa, turn on Ceiling Fan Light”
“Alexa, set Ceiling Fan to 1”
